contractObjectiveList.description: Attack the Installation and paint the area for a Fire Mission
contractObjectiveList.title: Attack the Installation and Place the Beacons for a Fire Mission

dialogueContent.words: Opening coms, looks like we have a serious situation here.
Go put the beepy things on the orange circles. We will handle the rest.
They are not going to like this, Expect reinforcements.
Gun Is charging, Wouldn't want it to go off too soon Commander.
By the way, if you are in the red triangle marked area when we shoot, You can expect to loose a mech or two.
When that thing goes 'Boom' Get to the evac area, I am not waiting long for you.
HAha! I will never get tired of that.
A Fortress protecting a Fortress, What is that Rogue AI doing that they need to protect it.
Whatever its doing it will be mine!
Seriously now, Fine I will do this myself.
We got the big gun charging, Expect a large explosion soon.
Ok but let us get our guys out of there.
Alpha beacon deployed, Commander. Good work.
Bravo beacon deployed, Commander.
Charlie beacon deployed.
We are under attack here, Please send reinforcements!
Get to the base and defend us now!
Don't let them place the beacons!
Fire Control this is Observer Actual: Good effect on target. Targets Destroyed.
Sometimes you have to do things yourself, Dropping.
Don't disappoint me.
I am out of here for now.
Time to raid some booty.
DO as I tell you to do and everything will be fine.
NO, NO, NO.. Defective parts from Bob again!
Commander, long-range sensors are picking up an enemy bogey. It'll be landing any minute.
I don't have any way to know where the enemy will land, but you can bet it will be close to the base.
Looks like they have a motorpool.
Take out the base and the motorpool will go BOOM!
Gun Is overcharged, We will be seeing an explosion soon.
OH goody, Reinforcements. They are lootboxes when you kill them!
Get out of here now!
Ah, Um.. Oops....
Warning: Incoming artillery fire.

longDescription: Great now we are going to free an AI that has gone mad. Does not anyone take the holo video warnings from the late 20th century seriously.

shortDescription: Ok we got some great information from the escort mission. First thing we learned was I hate escort missions, Secondly however is that this place serves two purposes one is to protect the AI on a near by planet, and It also has some nice loot.
